### 中止求解功能设计 (NEW)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 用户可以在求解过程中随时中止，系统返回当前最优解。

**API 设计:**

```
POST /api/v3/scheduling/cancel/:runId

Response:
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "求解已中止",
    "partialResult": { ... }  // 可选，返回当前最优解
}
```

**实现架构:**

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Frontend
    participant Node.js Backend
    participant V3 Solver (Python)
    
    Frontend->>Node.js Backend: POST /cancel/:runId
    Node.js Backend->>Node.js Backend: 设置 cancel_flag = true (Redis/DB)
    Node.js Backend-->>Frontend: { success: true }
    
    Note over V3 Solver: 求解循环中定期检查标志
    V3 Solver->>Node.js Backend: 检测到 cancel_flag
    V3 Solver->>Node.js Backend: 返回当前最优解
```

**Solver 端实现:**

```python
# solver_v3/core/engine.py
class SolverEngine:
    def solve(self, data, cancel_checker=None):
        # 在求解回调中检查中止标志
        def solution_callback(solution):
            if cancel_checker and cancel_checker():
                raise SolveCancelledException()
            # ... 正常处理
```

