### SSE 实时进度推送设计 (NEW)

> [!TIP]
> 使用 Server-Sent Events 实现低延迟的单向实时推送。

**架构选择:**

| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 | 选择 |
|------|------|------|------|
| **轮询** | 简单 | 延迟高、无效请求多 | ❌ |
| **WebSocket** | 双向、低延迟 | 需要维护连接 | ❌ |
| **SSE** | 单向推送、自动重连、HTTP兼容 | 仅支持文本 | ✅ |

**SSE 端点设计:**

```
GET /api/v3/scheduling/progress/:runId/stream
Content-Type: text/event-stream

event: progress
data: {"stage":"SOLVING","progress":45,"metrics":{...}}

event: objective
data: {"time":12.5,"value":-8500}

event: complete
data: {"status":"COMPLETED","result_url":"/api/v3/scheduling/result/123"}
```

**后端实现 (Node.js):**

```typescript
// backend/src/controllers/schedulingV3Controller.ts
export const progressStream = (req: Request, res: Response) => {
    const { runId } = req.params;
    
    res.setHeader('Content-Type', 'text/event-stream');
    res.setHeader('Cache-Control', 'no-cache');
    res.setHeader('Connection', 'keep-alive');
    
    const interval = setInterval(async () => {
        const status = await getRunStatus(runId);
        res.write(`event: progress\n`);
        res.write(`data: ${JSON.stringify(status)}\n\n`);
        
        if (status.status === 'COMPLETED' || status.status === 'FAILED') {
            clearInterval(interval);
            res.end();
        }
    }, 500);
    
    req.on('close', () => clearInterval(interval));
};
```

**前端使用:**

```typescript
// 使用 EventSource 订阅
const eventSource = new EventSource(`/api/v3/scheduling/progress/${runId}/stream`);

eventSource.addEventListener('progress', (event) => {
    const data = JSON.parse(event.data);
    setProgress(data.progress);
    setMetrics(data.metrics);
});

eventSource.addEventListener('complete', () => {
    eventSource.close();
    loadResult();
});
```

---

### 实时指标数据设计 (NEW)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 进度面板显示的指标需要从求解器实时计算并推送。

**指标定义:**

| 指标 | 字段名 | 计算方式 | 数据来源 |
|------|--------|----------|----------|
| 硬约束满足率 | `hard_constraint_satisfaction` | 已满足硬约束数/总硬约束数 | Solver回调 |
| 缺员操作数 | `understaffed_operations` | 未分配岗位数 | 当前解分析 |
| 共享组一致性 | `share_group_consistency` | 一致共享组/总共享组 | 当前解分析 |
| 公平性偏差 | `fairness_deviation` | max(夜班) - min(夜班) | 当前解分析 |
| 已找到解数 | `solutions_found` | 计数器累加 | 回调统计 |

**Solver 端收集指标:**

```python
# solver_v3/core/metrics_collector.py
class MetricsCollector:
    def __init__(self):
        self.solutions_found = 0
        self.best_objective = None
        
    def on_solution(self, solution, context):
        self.solutions_found += 1
        self.best_objective = solution.ObjectiveValue()
        
        # 分析当前解计算实时指标
        metrics = self.analyze_solution(solution, context)
        return metrics
    
    def analyze_solution(self, solution, context):
        return {
            "hard_constraint_satisfaction": self._calc_hard_satisfaction(),
            "understaffed_operations": self._count_understaffed(),
            "share_group_consistency": self._calc_share_consistency(),
            "fairness_deviation": self._calc_fairness(),
        }
```

**数据流:**

```
Solver 求解回调
    ↓
MetricsCollector.on_solution()
    ↓
写入 Redis/内存缓存 (run_id -> metrics)
    ↓
SSE 端点读取并推送
    ↓
前端 SolveProgressPanel 更新显示
```

